  --root ../../projects/<project-name>/../projects/<project-name> --round round-01 \
  --out projects/<project-name>/09_qa/robustness_checks.md
```

**6. Publication Readiness Score** (0-100%)

```bash
uv run ../../ma-end-to-end/scripts/publication_readiness_score.py \
  --root ../../projects/<project-name>/.. \
  --out projects/<project-name>/09_qa/readiness_score.md
```

**Score Components**:

- PRISMA checklist: 20%
- GRADE assessment: 15%
- Supplementary materials: 15%
- Author statements: 10%
- Claim audit: 15%
- Cross-reference validation: 10%
- Figure quality (DPI, labels): 10%
- Reference completeness: 5%

**Interpretation**:

- ≥95%: Ready to submit
- 85-94%: Almost ready (minor fixes)
- <85%: Major work needed

